cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and mapping sentences to formal queries. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a model that uses machine learning to perform the mapping task. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as the formal queries generated by the model are executed on a database. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a model that uses deep learning techniques. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with mapping natural language queries to formal queries that can be executed on a database, which is a task related to information retrieval.
